title: U.S. Patrols To Test China’s Pledge On South China Sea Islands
text: The U.S. determination to challenge China with patrols near Chinese-built islands in the South China Sea will test Xi Jinping’s recent pledge that Beijing doesn’t intend to “militarize” the islands, an announcement that took U.S. officials by surprise. -- This feed and its contents are the property of The Huffington Post, and use is subject to our terms.
